{"tid":1248534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三大紀律，八項注意！","createTime":"2019-06-21T13:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T06:28:11.000Z","uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59e32e2b41bba296c736918d5be8b6cbcfaefd83","tid":1248534,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"三大紀律：<br />\n<br />\n一切行動聽指揮；<br />\n不拿群眾一針一線；<br />\n一切繳獲要歸公。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八項注意：<br />\n<br />\n說話和氣；<br />\n買賣公平；<br />\n借東西要還；<br />\n損壞東西要賠償；<br />\n不打人罵人；<br />\n不損壞莊稼；<br />\n不調戲婦女；<br />\n不虐待俘虜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/三大纪律八项注意\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%BA%AA%E5%BE%8B%E5%85%AB%E9%A1%B9%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7e8503dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/三大纪律八项注意</a>"},{"pid":"ab96aeb970ef07cb30c8c8d8d673b487bb0d6dd5","tid":1248534,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"證明個班唔係解放軍<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港黑警</span></span>"},{"pid":"d419a9df10aef955bcab72e360c371b416d6ca00","tid":1248534,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"黑警可恥！"},{"pid":"d73239ed590387c3bb439513fe0ae1ec3748e22e","tid":1248534,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"反送中版有乜提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不流血、不受傷、不被捕<br />\n<br />\n一切傳聞要fact check<br />\n<br />\n保護傷者、保護記者<br />\n<br />\n緊急車輛必開路<br />\n<br />\nbe water 要流動<br />\n<br />\ntg 記緊nobody<br />\n<br />\n長輩圖、勤宣傳、勿圍爐<br />\n<br />\n不指責、不割蓆、兄弟爬山"}]}